    parentName: "blockquote"
  }, "III. Discipline")), mdx("p", null, "The cost of blowing off a day is much higher for part time. During your contiguous block, you have to be disciplined. Discipline comes with routine. If you can dedicate the same days every week, your mind snaps into focus more easily."), mdx("blockquote", null, mdx("p", {
    parentName: "blockquote"
